As a test of effectiveness, sensitivity analysis must be checked after the emergy evaluation in the system. So as to enhance the efficiency, it can be computed on account of emergy elerment error variation and the formula can be utilized as (1):1Em(i)=[(E+εe)×i]×[(T+εt)×i]\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
